       <narrative xml:lang="FR">By the end of 2022 :
- The country has a judicial case management system. 
&#x2022; The country has 4 full functioning courts (S&#xE3;o Tom&#xE9;, Angolares, Lemb&#xE1; e Pr&#xED;ncipe). 
&#x2022; The country has a Medico-Legal Office .</narrative>
      </comment>
     </target>
     <actual>
